data.description: The golf course is your neighbor, the monument your backdrop in this charming one-level home nestled along Tiara Rados #2 par 5 fairway on a quiet cul-de-sac. Sit on your sunny front deck for morning coffee or on the back under the shade of the pergola for a little respite after a round, And with a kitchen and master bath already remodeled with stainless, granite, and porcelain, you'll have plenty of time to work on your short game. With a location like this, your handicap is sure to go down! Not a golfer? Enjoy the rose garden, beautiful monument sunsets, and strolling through the park-like setting.
